Academic References
-------------------

The pitch control methodology is described in:
Spearman, W. (2018). "Beyond Expected Goals." MIT Sloan Sports
Analytics Conference.
See: http://www.sloansportsconference.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/2002.pdf

The ELASTIC event-tracking data synchronization methodology is
described in:
Kim, H. et al. (2025). "ELASTIC: Event-Level Alignment of
Synchronized Tracking and InferCed data."
See: https://arxiv.org/abs/2508.09238

This work itself is described in:
Lee, M. et al. (2026). "Valuing La Pausa: Quantifying Optimal Pass
Timing Beyond Speed." MIT Sloan Sports Analytics Conference.
See: https://github.com/leemingo/mitssac-pausa
